# Model weights and checkpoints
*.pt
*.pth
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.ckpt

# Checkpoint directories explicitly
checkpoints*/

# Training logs
runs/
logs/
wandb/

# Datasets (raw data, not vocab)
data/tinystories/*.arrow
data/tinystories/*.parquet
data/tinystories/train.txt
data/tinystories/val.txt

# Vocab — DO NOT ignore, keep in repo
# vocab.json

# Python environments
__pycache__/
venv/
env/
nanotales/
.env
```

---

## Key Changes
```
checkpoints*/     →  explicitly ignores checkpoints_rope,
                     checkpoints_gqa_rope, checkpoints_v2 etc
                     without needing to list each one

*.json removed    →  vocab.json will now be committed
*.txt tightened   →  only ignores the actual dataset txt files
                     not any other txt files you might add